# GeoCrossBench / Ï‡ViT â€” Project Knowledge

## What This Project Is

This is the codebase for the paper **GeoCrossBench: Cross-Band Generalization for Remote Sensing** (YerevaNN / UBC / Vector Institute). It evaluates how well remote sensing foundation models generalize across spectral bands (optical â†’ SAR, RGB â†’ multispectral superset, etc.) and introduces **Ï‡ViT (ChiViT)**, a ChannelViT variant pretrained with iBOT self-distillation that achieves best cross-band transfer.

