## Band System

### Sentinel-2 Bands Used (10 bands, â‰¤20m resolution)
`B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7, B8, B8A, B11, B12`

### Sentinel-1 SAR Bands
`VV, VH` (dual-polarization, absolute values)

### Standard Band Orderings (from `utils.py`)
- Default: `['B02','B03','B04','B05','B06','B07','B08','B8A','B11','B12','VH','VV']`
- Ï‡ViT pretrained: `['B04','B03','B02','B05','B06','B07','B08','B8A','B11','B12','VV','VH']` (RGB reversed)
- ChannelViT (so2sat): `['B02','B03','B04','B05','B06','B07','B08','B8A','B11','B12','VH','VH','VV','VV']` (duplicated SAR)
- CROMA: includes B01, B09
- Satlas: excludes B8A â†’ `['B02','B03','B04','B05','B06','B07','B08','B11','B12']`
- Prithvi: 6 bands â†’ `['B02','B03','B04','B8A','B11','B12']`

**CRITICAL**: Band ordering varies per model. Always use `get_band_orders(model_name)` from `utils.py`.

